creator: American Music Company
title: Nine Great American Women
description:
American women have made great contributions in a myriad of fields throughout the nation’s history. Some risked their lives for a cause, like former slave and abolitionist Harriet Tubman, or groundbreaking investigative journalist Nellie Bly. Others’ work shaped the world we live in today, like computer linguist Grace Hopper and pediatric cardiologist Helen B. Taussig. No short video could be comprehensive on this topic, but we hope it inspires you to celebrate the lives of the women who’ve made a positive impact on yours.

Discover more amazing and inspirational women: http://ow.ly/pk98309DjDG
